## 📱 Overview

**TRE Fit Life Wellness** is a freemium fitness tracking app that combines:
- 🗺️ GPS run/walk tracking with navigation
- ⚡ Real-time stats (distance, steps, pace, time)
- 💧 Smart hydration & nutrition reminders
- 🚧 Pro safety alerts (traffic & road blocks)
- 🛍️ Integrated shop (trendy.lk)
- ⭐ Freemium model with Pro features

---

## ✨ Features

### Free Version
- GPS tracking with map route visualization
- Step counter & distance tracking
- Live pace & time display
- Hydration/food reminders
- Shop integration (trendy.lk)

### Pro Version ($4.99/mo)
- Advanced safety alerts (traffic/road blocks)
- Premium workout plans
- Ad-free experience
- Priority support
- Advanced analytics

