## 🚀 Quick Start

### Prerequisites
- Node.js (v16+)
- npm or yarn
- Expo CLI
- iOS/Android phone with Expo Go app

### Installation

```bash
# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/TRE-Fit-Life-Wellness.git
cd TRE-Fit-Life-Wellness

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development server
npx expo start
